				\begin{document}$$-\,i\frac{d{a}_{n}}{dz}={V}_{v}{b}_{n},\quad -i\frac{d{c}_{n}}{dz}={V}_{h}({b}_{n+1}+{b}_{n}),\quad -i\frac{d{b}_{n}}{dz}={V}_{v}{a}_{n}+{V}_{h}({c}_{n}+{c}_{n-1}).$$\end{document}−idandz=Vvbn,−idcndz=Vh(bn+1+bn),−idbndz=Vvan+Vh(cn+cn−1).
